/a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Kennicott, Philip (December 7, 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/museums/work-by-martin-ramirez-key-outsider-artist-to-be-unveiled-at-library-of-congress/2013/12/07/3985668a-5e9e-11e3-95c2-13623eb2b0e1_story.html\">\"Work by Mart\u00edn Ram\u00edrez, key 'outsider artist,' to be unveiled at Library of Congress\"</a>. <i>The Washington Post</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Washington+Post&amp;rft.atitle=Work+by+Mart%C3%ADn+Ram%C3%ADrez%2C+key+%27outsider+artist%2C%27+to+be+unveiled+at+Library+of+Congress&amp;rft.date=2013-12-07&amp;rft.aulast=Kennicott&amp;rft.aufirst=Philip&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmuseums%2Fwork-by-martin-ramirez-key-outsider-artist-to-be-unveiled-at-library-of-congress%2F2013%2F12%2F07%2F3985668a-5e9e-11e3-95c2-13623eb2b0e1_story.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMart%C3%ADn+Ram%C3%ADrez\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/26/arts/design/26rami.html?ref=museumofamericanfolkart\">https://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/26/arts/design/26rami.html?ref=museumofamericanfolkart</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://about.usps.com/news/national-releases/2015/pr15_018.htm\">https://about.usps.com/news/national-releases/2015/pr15_018.htm</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-12\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://observer.com/2011/10/deeper-into-martin-ramirezs-world-an-outsider-masters-vision-in-never-before-seen-drawings/2/\">http://observer.com/2011/10/deeper-into-martin-ramirezs-world-an-outsider-masters-vision-in-never-before-seen-drawings/2/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://observer.com/2011/10/deeper-into-martin-ramirezs-world-an-outsider-masters-vision-in-never-before-seen-drawings/2/\">http://observer.com/2011/10/deeper-into-martin-ramirezs-world-an-outsider-masters-vision-in-never-before-seen-drawings/2/</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Kennicott, Philip (December 7, 2013). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/museums/work-by-martin-ramirez-key-outsider-artist-to-be-unveiled-at-library-of-congress/2013/12/07/3985668a-5e9e-11e3-95c2-13623eb2b0e1_story.html\">\"Work by Mart\u00edn Ram\u00edrez, key 'outsider artist,' to be unveiled at Library of Congress\"</a>. <i>The Washington Post</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Washington+Post&amp;rft.atitle=Work+by+Mart%C3%ADn+Ram%C3%ADrez%2C+key+%27outsider+artist%2C%27+to+be+unveiled+at+Library+of+Congress&amp;rft.date=2013-12-07&amp;rft.aulast=Kennicott&amp;rft.aufirst=Philip&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmuseums%2Fwork-by-martin-ramirez-key-outsider-artist-to-be-unveiled-at-library-of-congress%2F2013%2F12%2F07%2F3985668a-5e9e-11e3-95c2-13623eb2b0e1_story.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedi